div.div: Nageki no Bourei wa Intai Shitai

Six childhood friends make a vow one day to become treasure hunters, and eventually grow to be the strongest heroes in the world. During his first quest, Krai Andrey realizes he isnt cut out for the job. Even so, his friends make him their leader. Underpowered in the face of great expectations, Krai embarks on a reluctant heros tale of glory, headaches, and wanting to retire early.
(Source: Crunchyroll)

LycoReco is a caf with a traditional Japanese twist located in downtown Tokyo. But the delicious coffee and sugary sweets are not the only orders this caf takes! From delivering packages short distances, to pick-ups and drop-offs on the lonely streets at night, to zombies and giant monster extermination?! Whatever your problem, we're here to help! We will solve any kind of "trouble" you may have!
Waiting for you are the ever-smiling poster-girl and the cool, serious newcomer. A petite girl who never wants to work and a young woman approaching thirty who wants to get married. And the manager is a nice guy whos obsessed with Japan!
Whatever your order is, leave it all up to us
(Source: Official Site)

Leticia Dorman is living every girls dreamshes the daughter of a duke whos grown up in the lap of luxury and shes engaged to none other than the handsome crown prince, Clarke. But this dream is her nightmare! In preparation to become part of the royal family, Lettie has endured ten painful years of lessons on everything from dancing to etiquette. Her only chance of escape lies in the prince breaking off their engagement, which seems unlikelyuntil he shows up at a royal ball with a mysterious woman. This could be her chance to break free, but not if Prince Clarke has anything to say about it!
(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)
Tsuihou Sareta Onimotsu Tamer, Sekai Yuiitsu no Necromancer ni Kakusei Suru: The Tale of the Necromancer.

Recon, mapping, carrying baggage, cooking, keeping watch, taking blows even while doing all these things, the tamer, Randall, is called a burden and useless by his party members.
This S-ranked party is filled with genius magicians, excellent swordsmen, famous priests, and great knights, that show superb teamwork and drive, which helped them become the most famous party in the country.
But despite being incredibly popular, the members of the party feel dissatisfied with Randall. He soon gets kicked out just while he was gaining influence of his own and unlocks his true power while seeking for his revenge.
